== DVD release ==
Individual box sets for series one, two, and three were released on 9 September 2013,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bad-Education-DVD-Jack-Whitehall/dp/B0089KSLUY/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&colid=1EJZQ2SZLIMZR&coliid=I17TJL0P8977M7 |title=<nowiki>Bad Education [DVD</nowiki>&#93; |publisher=Amazon.co.uk |accessdate=30 July 2013}}</ref> 29 September 2014,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bad-Education-Series-Two-DVD/dp/B00M94YQS2/ref=sr_1_12?s=dvd&ie=UTF8&qid=1407410090&sr=1-12&keywords=bad+education|title=Bad Education – Series 2 [DVD]|website=Amazon.co.uk}}</ref> and 31 August 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=Bad Education - Series 3 [DVD]|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bad-Education-DVD-Jack-Whitehall/dp/B011VCLPY0/ref=sr_1_5?s=dvd&ie=UTF8&qid=1508829286&sr=1-5&keywords=bad+education|website=Amazon.co.uk|accessdate=24 October 2017}}</ref> respectively.

A box set containing both the first and second series of ''Bad Education'' was released on DVD on 29 September 2014.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bad-Education-Series-And-DVD/dp/B00M94YQNM/ref=pd_sim_sbs_d_h__3?ie=UTF8&refRID=06KHT398JKV2PFCXPKWK|title=Bad Education – Series 1-2 [DVD] [2012]|website=Amazon.co.uk}}</ref>

A box set containing all three series was made available on 31 August 2015.

