{{Expand Ukrainian|Номерні знаки Домініки|date=March 2018}} [[Dominica]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/CA_DOMI.html</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle_registration_plates_of_the_United_States#Designs_and_serial_formats|North American standard]] 6 × 12 inches (152 × 300 mm). Vehicles have black on white plates (front and rear) or black on white (front) and black on yellow (rear) plates.<ref>http://plaque.free.fr/ca/wd/</ref>
