'''Đurđekovec''' is a settlement in the City of [[Zagreb]], [[Croatia]], population 778 (2011).<ref>{{Croatian Census 2011|S|21}}</ref> It is located around 9&nbsp;km north-east of the city centre of Zagreb and adjacent to the [[Medvednica]] mountain.

